<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Beranda' }) %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-brim-navy text-white overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-brim-gold via-brim-navy to-brim-navy">
        </div>
        <div
            class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 py-24 md:py-32 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight"
                data-aos="fade-up">
                Membangun <span class="text-brim-gold">Intelektualitas</span><br /> Berbasis Riset & Spiritualitas
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mb-8 sm:mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed px-2 sm:px-0"
                data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
                Badan Riset dan Intelektual Mahasantri Khatamun Nabiyyin <br> mencetak kader kritis, kreatif, dan
                berakhlak mulia.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row w-full sm:w-auto gap-3 sm:gap-4 px-4 sm:px-0" data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-delay="100">
                <a href="#tentang"
                    class="bg-brim-gold text-brim-navy px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-yellow-500 transition shadow-lg w-full sm:w-auto text-center">Pelajari
                    Lebih Lanjut</a>
                <a href="/blog"
                    class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-brim-navy transition shadow-lg w-full sm:w-auto text-center">Baca
                    Artikel</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="tentang" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-brim-navy mb-4">Tentang BRIM KN</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brim-gold mx-auto rounded-full mb-8"></div>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-4">
                    BRIM (Badan Riset dan Intelektual Mahasantri) adalah sebuah organisasi resmi milik <strong>Pesantren
                        Khatamun Nabiyyin</strong>. Dirancang sebagai platform yang mendorong mahasantri untuk aktif
                    dalam penelitian, penulisan ilmiah, diskusi akademik, serta pengembangan gagasan inovatif. Selain
                    itu, lembaga ini juga diarahkan untuk membangun jejaring keilmuan, baik di lingkungan pesantren
                    maupun dengan institusi eksternal.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16 items-start">
                <div class="bg-brim-gray p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition"
                    data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brim-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brim-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-brim-navy mb-4">Visi</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                        Menjadi wadah pembinaan mahasantri yang unggul dalam intelektualitas, spiritualitas, riset
                        ilmiah, dan pengabdian sosial berdasarkan nilai-nilai Islam Muhammadi dan Ahlulbait.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-brim-gray p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition"
                    data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brim-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brim-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-brim-navy mb-4">Misi</h3>
                    <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 text-gray-600 space-y-3">
                        <li>Mengembangkan budaya riset, literasi, dan kajian ilmiah di kalangan mahasantri.</li>
                        <li>Membentuk karakter mahasantri yang disiplin, berakhlak, dan aktif kreatif inovatif.</li>
                        <li>Mencetak kader intelektual Islam yang kritis, kreatif, dan bertanggung jawab.</li>
                        <li>Mengoptimalkan media dan teknologi sebagai sarana dakwah dan edukasi.</li>
                        <li>Menumbuhkan semangat pengabdian sosial dan ukhuwah antar intelektual muda.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-brim-navy text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden"
                data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-brim-gold rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-8 text-center text-brim-gold">Tujuan Kami</h3>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brim-gold mb-2 opacity-50">01</div>
                            <p class="font-medium text-lg">Membina intelektualitas mahasantri</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brim-gold mb-2 opacity-50">02</div>
                            <p class="font-medium text-lg">Mengembangkan budaya riset dan literasi</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brim-gold mb-2 opacity-50">03</div>
                            <p class="font-medium text-lg">Membentuk kader berakhlak dan disiplin</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
                            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brim-gold mb-2 opacity-50">04</div>
                            <p class="font-medium text-lg">Mengoptimalkan pengabdian sosial dan dakwah</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Latest Articles Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-brim-gray">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center sm:items-end mb-12 border-b pb-4 border-gray-200"
                data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="text-center sm:text-left mb-4 sm:mb-0">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-brim-navy">Artikel Terbaru</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Berita, opini, dan hasil riset</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/blog"
                    class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-brim-navy hover:text-brim-gold transition">
                    Lihat Semua <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <% if (posts && posts.length> 0) { %>
                    <% posts.forEach((post, index)=> { %>
                        <article
                            class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1"
                            data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="<%= index * 50 %>">
                            <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-brim-gold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                                    <%= new Date(post.created_at).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: 'numeric' ,
                                        month: 'long' , year: 'numeric' }) %>
                                </div>
                                <h3
                                    class="text-xl font-bold text-brim-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition leading-snug">
                                    <a href="/blog/<%= post.slug %>">
                                        <%= post.title %>
                                    </a>
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow line-clamp-3">
                                    <%= post.meta_description || post.content.replace(/<[^>]+>/g, '').substring(0, 150)
                                        + '...' %>
                                </p>
                                <a href="/blog/<%= post.slug %>"
                                    class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-brim-navy hover:text-brim-gold transition mt-auto">
                                    Baca Selengkapnya <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                        viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                            d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <% }) %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <div
                                    class="col-span-3 text-center py-12 text-gray-500 bg-white rounded-xl border border-dashed border-gray-300">
                                    Belum ada artikel yang dipublikasikan.
                                </div>
                                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10 text-center sm:hidden">
                <a href="/blog"
                    class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-brim-navy bg-white border border-gray-300 px-6 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 transition">
                    Lihat Semua Artikel
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>